<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA88">
<l>iruḷi ṉuruveṉkō māmēka meṉkō</l>
<l>maruḷiṉ maṇinīla meṉkō - varuḷemakku</l>
<l>naṉṟuṭaiyāy ceñcaṭaimē ṉakkilaṅku veṇmatiya</l>
<l>moṉṟuṭaiyāy kaṇṭat toḷi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I say form of darkness? Will I say great cloud?</l>
<l>Will I say flawless sapphire blueness – of the light</l>
<l>in the throat of you who possess one smiling shining white moon</l>
<l>on [your] red matted hair, you who well possess grace for us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
